“The Beautiful Habano” like the one in my hand a @habanos_oficial San Cristobal 
El Principe, a light smoke to kick off the day! 
Life is Beautiful 🙏🏻🌊🇨🇺🔥

node.text:
“THE BEAUTIFUL HABANO” 🇨🇺💨
an In-Depth Biography of Tobacco 
is the name of the book that I been reading for a while… 
Slowly enjoying in every corner of it, usually with some Havana cigar in my hand! This time with epic @habanos_oficial HDM Río Seco 
next to the Adriatic Sea 🌊 
The Book is Amazing work of Reynaldo Gonzáles 💨🇨🇺
Life is Beautiful 🙏🏻
